    {
      "id": "68",
      "name": "Lore",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Description",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Personality",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Flora loves flowers. She has a Bloatty Floatty imaginary friend who she calls \"Mr. Floaty.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Appearance",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Flora has short blonde hair and blue-green eyes. She wears a pink and white dress with a white headband, long white socks and brown Mary Jane shoes.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Dialogue",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Welcome to Floral Whisper. Do you need anything?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "I. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "About Stormterror...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "It's great that I don't have to worry about the flowers in my store being blown away by the wind.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "That said, the Dandelion Seeds have also been blown all across the region of Mondstadt by this storm. Who knows, perhaps they will bloom throughout the land.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "When I think about it like that, the storm doesn't seem so scary anymore, haha.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "II. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tell me about your flowers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "We carry a large variety of flowers. Are you looking for anything in particular?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "I. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tell me about Dandelions.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Dandelions are so feathery. They are my personal favorite.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The Acting Grand Master of the Knights is also known as the Dandelion Knight, as I recall.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "She probably learned the power of Anemo from the dandelions, hehe.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "I. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Why do you like Dandelions so much?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Hehe, I wonder... Maybe it's because I've been reading The Fox in the Dandelion Sea.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Here, take it. Maybe you'll like dandelions too once you finish reading it, hehe.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "II. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tell me about Sweet Flowers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Sweet Flowers, you say?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "They look nice, but most people just use them for cooking.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "If you see people having Sweet Flowers in their gardens...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "They are probably used to get sugar.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "III. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tell me about Cecilias.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Cecilias! You've got good taste.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "They grow in cold and windy places. Legend has it they only bloom when it's quiet.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "If you wish to cultivate them...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "You'll probably have better luck with Mist Flowers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "III. Traveler:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Sorry for bothering you.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "You need to go?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Flora:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "I'll tell you more about flowers next time if you like.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Voice-Overs",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Voice Over I",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dandelions?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Voice Over II",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Well, if it's an injury...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Attributes",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Story Quest(s)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Carmen Dei Chapter (Venti)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Act I: Should You Be Trapped in a Windless Land",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "italic"
